title: Goat Cheese & Prosciutto Toasts with Arugula & Hot Honey
description: The best thing since sliced bread? Sliced and toasted bread loaded up with flavors we love! For this light lunch, sourdough is toasted until golden, then spread with tangy goat cheese. Next, you’ll add color and crunch with thinly sliced cukes and a handful of peppery, lemon-kissed arugula. Drape with salty-savory prosciutto, and top it all off with a drizzle of hot honey for a kick of sweet heat. It’s truly a toast with the most!
